 in your community we would be happy to provide a market analysis for your review if you would like more information about partnering with healthsouth or would like to schedule a meeting please call    or email us at partnershiphealthsouthcom becoming a healthsouth vendor healthsouth partners with a diverse supplier base that offer products or services that meet the needs of a large integrated delivery network of inpatient rehabilitation hospitals across the country  healthsouth focuses on utilizing our group purchasing organization medassets for most supplyrelated contracts the medassets program offers contracting opportunities with manufacturers distributors and service providers that are certified as minorityowned femaleowned veteranowned and small disadvantagedowned businesses healthsouth also aims to work with suppliers that can handle electronic transactions to improve the control and compliance of our supplyrelated expenses  if you are interested in partnering with healthsouth please click here to go to the medassets website and apply to be their supplier or email feedbackhealthsouthcom to gain more information on healthsouth’s needs click here to go to the medassets website and apply investor relations visit our investor relations site to view our company profile stock information news and more media hotline members of the media requesting information or an interview can call   questions visit our frequently asked questions section or use the form below to contact us first name please enter your first name last name please enter your last name email  findlocation box search by state address is required select a service type rehab hospital encompass home health outpatient rehabilitation clinics show all facilities by type contact us healthsouth  grandview parkway suite  birmingham al  main office  facility information    find a location investors employees calendars contact us font size small big print share   english  español healthsouth search form location